The paper discusses the application of edge computing, caching, and communication in the field of IoT, which falls under the category of networked and distributed systems (cs.NI). The paper also proposes the use of AI technology in this context, which suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The algorithm proposed in the paper involves joint optimization of computation offloading, caching, and wireless communication, indicating a potential fit for the categories of distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and control systems (cs.SY).
